OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy shares 'shock' cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,FThe former Team GB cyclist is
OL,7,Fcurrently undergoing treatment,
OL,8,Fincluding chemotherapy
OL,10,FOlympic gold medal winner Sir Chris
OL,11,FHoy has announced he has been
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with cancer.
OL,14,FThe former Team GB cyclist is
OL,15,Fcurrently undergoing treatment,
OL,16,Fincluding chemotherapy, he said in an
OL,17,FInstagram post.
