OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy shares 'shock' cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,FThe 47-year-old said he had hoped to
OL,7,Fkeep his diagnosis private due to his
OL,8,F"young family" but had shared the
OL,9,Fhealth update as his "hand had been
OL,10,Fforced".
OL,12,FIn an Instagram post, Sir Chris said:
OL,13,F"I have a bit of news. Last year I was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with cancer, which came as a
OL,15,Fhuge shock, having had no symptoms up
OL,16,Fto that point.
OL,18,F"I'm currently receiving treatment
OL,19,Fincluding chemotherapy, which
OL,20,Fthankfully is going really well.
