OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy shares 'shock' cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,F"I'd like to extend my sincere
OL,7,Fgratitude to all the medical
OL,8,Fprofessionals for their amazing help
OL,9,Fand care."
OL,11,FThe Scot added: "I'm optimistic,
OL,12,Fpositive and surrounded by love for
OL,13,Fwhich I'm truly grateful. As you might
OL,14,Fimagine, the last few months have been
OL,15,Fincredibly difficult.
OL,17,F"However I currently feel fine - I am
OL,18,Fcontinuing to work, ride my bike and
OL,19,Flive my life as normal."
